// ContextMenu (diagram)
// Floating context menu for diagram node and edge elements in edit mode.
// Shows different actions depending on the element type:
//   Nodes: Edit Description, Add Transition, Delete Node
//   Edges: Edit Label, Change Origin, Change Destination, Delete Arrow
// Closes on click outside or Escape.

FUNCTION ContextMenu(x, y, type, targetId, onClose, onEditLabel, onChangeType, onDelete, onChangeOrigin, onChangeDest, onAddTransition) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Positioned at (x, y) via fixed CSS.
  Closes on mousedown outside menu ref. Closes on Escape key.

---

FUNCTION handleMenuItemClick(callback) -> void
  Calls callback(targetId) then calls onClose().
